[color=#00ffff]Description:
[/color][/center][list]
[*]This mod is a body preset to CBBE. All credit for the software, textures, and meshes used go to Caliente.

[*]This is my first mod. More content soon to come if I enjoy this. More Skyrim and Fallout 4 mods may come.
[*]There will be no more updates for this version.
[/list]
[center][u][color=#00ffff][size=6]Thank you

[/size][/color][/u][i]Just a quick thank you note to Caliente and Bethesda for being able to make easy to understand software. Hopefully this will start my career for modding.[/i][/center]
